<ul class="faq">
  <li class="q">Q: How much does the initial consultation cost?</li>
  <li class="a">
    <a class="toggle-answer" href="#" onclick="showFaqAnswer(this); return false;">Show Answer</a>
    <div class="answer" style="display: none;">

      <p class="answer">A: Nothing at all. The initial consultation is on us. It takes as little as
      15-20 minutes, we just like to meet you in person, preferably at your offices so we can get a
      feel for what your company is like. We ask a few questions to find out what kind of solution
      would best meet your needs, and you can of course ask us questions about our company and
      services.</p>

    </div>
  </li>
</ul>

