<ul class="faq">
  <li class="q">Q: Which tasks are considered maintenance, and which are billable enhancements?</li>
  <li class="a">
    <a class="toggle-answer" href="#" onclick="showFaqAnswer(this); return false;">Show Answer</a>
    <div class="answer" style="display: none;">

      <p>A: Compared to many other web site companies, we are very liberal with our definition of
      maintenance. Very broadly, anything that would create a new use or a new audience for your web
      site would be considered an enhancement. Everything else (generally adding/updating/removing
      content) is considered maintenance.</p>

      <p>In the trickier cases, we will make the call on a case-by-case basis whether the requested
      task is considered to be maintenance, and if the task is deemed an enhancement, we will give
      you a time and cost estimate before proceeding.</p>

    </div>
  </li>
</ul>

